## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `flutter analyze` to ensure zero lint issues.
- Run `flutter test` to execute newly added test scenarios.

### Manual Verification
- Build and run the app to ensure no breaking changes were introduced during code cleanup.
- Verify that error handling works as expected.
